&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a Strategic Account Executive (APAC) to lead the implementation of advanced Treasury and Risk Management solutions within our global finance network. This critical position suits a professional who understands that treasury’s future blends traditional management with blockchain-based digital assets. You will drive the generation and closure of high-value enterprise deals while demonstrating how Ripple Treasury delivers capital efficiency, real-time insight, and automated liquidity. The ideal candidate possesses deep expertise in core treasury roles—such as global cash oversight, multi-currency liquidity handling, and financial risk control—and can illustrate how blockchain and digital assets enhance traditional finance by eliminating fragmented legacy workflows.&lt;/p&gt;
