&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as the primary strategic lead for a portfolio of high-value enterprise accounts. Manage complex sales cycles and align Ripple’s global treasury roadmap with large corporate financial goals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Whitespace Analysis and Revenue Optimization: Perform detailed whitespace analysis within the enterprise tier to uncover untapped opportunities for cross-selling and up-selling sophisticated treasury and risk management modules.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strategic Pursuit and Expansion: Drive aggressive revenue growth by converting identified whitespace into high-contract-value business, growing Ripple’s footprint across global subsidiaries and diverse business units.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comprehensive Account Sales Planning: Develop and maintain multi-year account plans that map intricate collaborator hierarchies, budget cycles, and technical roadmaps to ensure a predictable, high-performing sales pipeline.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain a high &quot;share of voice&quot; with CFOs, Global Treasurers, and Heads of Risk. Position Ripple Treasury as the central nervous system for their institutional liquidity and risk operations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deal Leadership and Negotiation: Act as the &quot;CEO of the Deal.&quot; Coordinate cross-functional teams across legal, product, and compliance. Navigate procurement hurdles in enterprise-grade financial software sales successfully.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
