&lt;p&gt;Your responsibility is to exclusively win new corporate clients for Ripple Treasury. This role requires effective positioning of a curated selection of the Ripple Treasury Platform&#39;s core capabilities to each target account, with end-to-end accountability for territory development and full deal lifecycle management.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you’re ready to see your impact and unlock incredible career growth opportunities, join us, and build real world value.&lt;/p&gt;
