&lt;li&gt;Reconcile on-chain and off-chain positions against custodian statements and internal trading system data.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide support for accounting related to digital asset lending, repo, and collateral arrangements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
