&lt;li&gt;Maintain and improve internal control procedures, including SOD documentation and reconciliation sign-off protocols.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate in systems and process improvement initiatives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
