&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a strategic Brand Designer who pays attention to detail. As a member of the Brand Studio, you&#39;ll collaborate across teams to develop brand experiences with Ripple and XRP—from concept through completion—translating concepts into compelling visual work that solves unique challenges.&lt;/p&gt;
