&lt;li&gt;A sharp eye for detail and the ability to stay organized and solve problems in a fast-moving environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with payment services, collections, markets, and instruments (e.g. OTC, crypto, derivatives) and core reconciliation principles&lt;/li&gt;
